<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
	<link href = "https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
	<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
	<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../music.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../style.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../chat.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../profile.css">
</head>

<body>
	<%- include("navbar") %>
	<%- include("music") %>

	<div id="profile">
		<div id="resources">
			<h1><%= name %>'s Profile</h1>
			<h3>Mental Health Resources</h3>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="https://mhanational.org/">Mental Health America</a>:  Mental Health America is dedicated to the promotion of mental health, well-being, and condition prevention. Their website includes information about mental health and online screenings.</li> 
				<li><a href="988lifeline.org">Suicide and Crisis Hotline</a>:  If you or someone you know is experiencing mental health or substance use-related crisis, the Lifeline network is available 24/7.</li>
				<li><a href="https://www.samhsa.gov/mental-health">Substance Abuse and Mental Health Services Administration</a>:  The agencey within the U.S. Department of Health and Human Services that leads public health efforts by making substance use and mental disorder information, services, and research more accessible.</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div id="charts">
			<canvas class="chart" id="emotions"></canvas>
			<canvas class="chart" id="sentiments"></canvas>
		</div>
	
		<div id="activities">
			<h3>Ideas to Improve Happiness</h3>
			<ul id="activitiesList">
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>


	<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
	
	<script src="../js/emotionchart.js" onload="createCharts('<%= emotions %>', '<%= sentiments %>', '<%= activities %>')"></script>
	<script src="../js/profile.js" onload="loadList('<%= activities %>')"></script>

	<script src="../js/music.js" defer></script>
	<script src="../js/chat.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>